    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a one-time password authentication system (OTP).  The system provides authentication for system access (login) and other applications requiring authentication that is secure against passive attacks based on replaying captured reusable passwords. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
